text: Ineta Mackeviča (born 11 July 1992 in Liepaja) is a Latvian professional squash player. As of February 2018, she was ranked number 84 in the world. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Latvian female squash players Category:Sportspeople from Liepāja
title: Ineta Mackeviča
